Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.57,0:22:24.68,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}あたまポフポフしてよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.30,0:22:28.41,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}あなたの袖をつかみ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.08,0:22:32.63,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}ピコピコしたらなでて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.86,0:22:35.06,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}ゴロゴロしたいの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.62,0:22:40.14,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}心配してにゃいのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.44,0:22:43.66,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}少し気になるだけよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.22,0:22:47.98,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}ニヨニヨしたらそっと
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.08,0:22:50.29,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}背中借りるから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.77,0:22:58.41,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}いつまでも　不器用なままよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.61,0:23:04.77,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}こっち向いてよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.40,0:23:07.45,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}好き…って言えない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.86,0:23:09.36,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}そばにいて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.36,0:23:23.07,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}あなたのことを獨り占めしたいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.88,0:23:28.81,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}素直になれないの
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.85,0:23:30.93,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}だけどね
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.46,0:23:37.60,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}繋いていいからね
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.71,0:23:43.84,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}手をギュしてね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.57,0:22:24.68,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}頭腦昏昏漲漲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.30,0:22:28.41,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}抓住你的袖子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.08,0:22:32.63,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}你緩緩地撫摸我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.86,0:22:35.06,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}好想就這麼悠閒下去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.62,0:22:40.14,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}不要那麼擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.44,0:22:43.66,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}只是有點在意罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.22,0:22:47.98,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}微笑著 輕輕地
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.08,0:22:50.29,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}靠在了背上
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.77,0:22:58.41,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}一直都這麼地笨拙
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.61,0:23:04.77,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}向這邊看過了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.40,0:23:07.45,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}喜歡 說不出口
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.86,0:23:09.36,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}留在我身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.36,0:23:23.07,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}好想把你獨佔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.88,0:23:28.81,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}雖然無法變得坦率
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.85,0:23:30.93,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}但是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.46,0:23:37.60,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}牽起來就夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.71,0:23:43.84,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}緊緊握著我的手
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.88,0:00:46.18,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}one two three four
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.18,0:00:48.51,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}one two three four
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.41,0:01:06.20,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}戀の意味なんかわからない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.26,0:01:09.51,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}あなたを見つめてたい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.07,0:01:11.04,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\an9}素直にならないお年頃？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.64,0:01:15.21,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}わかっているのかいないのか
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.21,0:01:19.81,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}最大のミステリーだだだだだだだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.81,0:01:24.64,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}一人きり　過ごす日は
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.64,0:01:29.33,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}ちょっぴり何か足りなくて　
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.33,0:01:31.24,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}みんながそろうと
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.60,0:01:33.61,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}やっぱり楽しい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.87,0:01:38.53,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}今は さあ 遊んじゃえ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.03,0:01:43.22,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}あっちで手を取って
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.31,0:01:45.36,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}こっちで大騒ぎ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.44,0:01:47.81,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}この後のハーモニー
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.81,0:01:50.08,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}みんなで奏でる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.08,0:01:52.39,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}あっちで落ち著いて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.51,0:01:54.54,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}こっちでひと休み
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.64,0:01:59.59,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}心はぽかぽかして
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.93,0:02:08.71,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}君がそばにいる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.88,0:00:46.18,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}one two three four
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.18,0:00:48.51,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}one two three four
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.41,0:01:06.20,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我不懂所謂的戀愛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.26,0:01:09.51,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}只想一直注視著你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.07,0:01:11.04,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\an1}無法坦率的年齡？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.64,0:01:15.21,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}到底是明白還是不明白呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.21,0:01:19.81,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}這是最大的謎題
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.81,0:01:24.64,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}孤獨度過的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.64,0:01:29.33,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}總感覺少了點什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.33,0:01:31.24,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}大家聚在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.60,0:01:33.61,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}真的很快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.87,0:01:38.53,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}現在 走 去玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.03,0:01:43.22,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}在那裡牽著手
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.31,0:01:45.36,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}在這裡很熱鬧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.44,0:01:47.81,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}之後的協奏曲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.81,0:01:50.08,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}由大家來演奏
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.08,0:01:52.39,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}在那裡很安逸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.51,0:01:54.54,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}在這裡稍稍休息
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.64,0:01:59.59,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}心裡暖烘烘的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.93,0:02:08.71,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}因為有你陪伴
